<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Help Telling Your Story</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #2a7ae2;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>If you're not sure how to explain what happened during the years
            you were behind, or if you’re struggling to figure out what
            documents support your hardship, you’re not alone. We can help.</p>
          <p>We’ll schedule a one-on-one phone call where all you need to do is
            walk us through your story. Just tell us what you remember from
            those years—what made it difficult to file or pay on time. We’ll
            help you identify which details are most relevant and guide you on
            what documentation can help prove your case.</p>
          <p>This is about giving them a complete and honest picture of your
            situation. We’ll make sure it’s clear, organized, and submitted
            properly.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call us at
            <a
              href="tel:{{phone}}"
              style="color: #2a7ae2; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{phone}}</a>, and we’ll help you through it.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>